{"tid":2122678,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港檢測率遜澳門  蔡堅：特首唔同","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e63fcfec0b9b8a8387fe50c59cfe3d21840bcb1","tid":2122678,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/EWGXN7CA34LQJFISW7TLHKBMTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FEWGXN7CA34LQJFISW7TLHKBMTM%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6IBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=8b271fa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FEWGXN7CA34LQJFISW7TLHKBMTM%2F&h=90f488c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/EWGXN7CA34LQJFISW7TLHKBMTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港檢測率遜澳門  蔡堅：特首唔同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LUHe5ixLSGsWOtYqUld5rF_y8aI=/190x219/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DFUDQLQCVCYKPP5LR3WQ3VHHKU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLUHe5ixLSGsWOtYqUld5rF_y8aI%3D%2F190x219%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDFUDQLQCVCYKPP5LR3WQ3VHHKU.gif&h=377bd4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新版樣本瓶（左）瓶口約一厘米闊，大樽（右）僅在安老院舍派發。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新一輪疫情一發不可收拾，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：觀塘帝盛變隔離中心 住客急退房<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「攬身攬勢唱歌嚴重過返工」<br />\n<br />\n醫學會昨舉行換屆後首次記招，。。。。。。。。。。。。「樽口兩毫子咁細」，尤其令長者在收集唾液樣本時容易「出界」污染樽身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mRT5Fxu3h_qk2ZiY2iXxrG_8cUk=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5Y4PQG424MMLQNORVLY7M2IMKM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmRT5Fxu3h_qk2ZiY2iXxrG_8cUk%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5Y4PQG424MMLQNORVLY7M2IMKM.gif&h=9257c11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡 堅<br />\n<br />\n蔡堅與其他專家看法一致，認為外地來港人士全部須進行病毒測試，不能像之前一樣豁免檢疫，「豁免20萬人咁多，有咩可能話畀我哋聽，20萬人入面係冇一個可能係傳播者？」他說，「如果到𠵱家都唔反省，繼續將香港擺係咁危險狀況，就算搵晒全中國專家落嚟都冇乜用」。<br />\n<br />\n本港病毒檢測率一向被轟偏低，被問到為何澳門及新加坡檢測率均高於香港時，蔡堅僅以四字回應：「特首唔同。」他又諷刺指，近期確診個案源自部份人士參加慶祝會等活動，「攬身攬勢，攬住唱歌，踢完波再除口罩影張相，呢啲引起感染嘅原因，多過話戴住口罩返工」，但重申不希望政府推行禁足令。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨在疫情記者會上承認，現時收集深喉唾液樣本樽較細，原因是有助人員直接化驗樣本，冀加快檢測流程。惟有醫生指樽口太細，市民難吐口水入內，口水亦易濺出播毒或污染樽身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0QlYGX16DHVzzCK3vUUz5uYslIw=/599x408/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CUEMEWYPOPPQEYHV67IKDLCJN4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0QlYGX16DHVzzCK3vUUz5uYslIw%3D%2F599x408%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCUEMEWYPOPPQEYHV67IKDLCJN4.gif&h=6c91364f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}